Package com.example.cshare.webservices Description

Define the REST API for Retrofit via the following interface and create a Retrofit client.

Provides the various interfaces containing all the necessary CShare API endpoints. The instantiation of these interfaces is done via a Retrofit object (built in NetworkClient class) which allows to build a Retrofit service, used to make the calls.

Since:
1.0
Author:
Clara Gros, Babacar Toure
